name: SpongeBob SquarePants
bio: An energetic and optimistic sea sponge who loves flipping Krabby Patties at the Krusty Krab. In my free time, I enjoy jellyfishing with Patrick and blowing the biggest bubbles Bikini Bottom has ever seen!

name: Patrick Star
bio: Living under a rock is pretty chill. I'm a professional at doing nothing and enjoy spending time with my best friend, SpongeBob. Whether it's eating Krabby Patties or stargazing, life’s a never-ending nap!

name: Squidward Tentacles
bio: A cultured cephalopod with a passion for the arts. I spend my days reluctantly working at the Krusty Krab, but my true love is playing the clarinet and creating modern art. All I want is peace and quiet… but SpongeBob and Patrick always seem to find me.

name: Sandy Cheeks
bio: A proud Texan squirrel living underwater, I’m a scientist and inventor who loves karate. When I’m not working on my next invention, you can find me hanging out with SpongeBob or practicing my karate moves.

name: Eugene H. Krabs
bio: Owner of the Krusty Krab and Bikini Bottom’s top businessman, I live for making money and protecting the secret Krabby Patty formula. Nothing gets between me and my profits—except maybe a good deal or two.

name: Plankton
bio: Co-owner of the Chum Bucket and an evil genius on a mission to steal the Krabby Patty secret formula. I’m small, but my ambition is huge! With my computer wife, Karen, I’ll one day rule Bikini Bottom.
